title: New coach Campbell says Dolphins need a change in culture
text: > Florida New coach Campbell says Dolphins need a change in culture Former Miami Dolphins tight ends coach Dan Campbell, foreground, gestures as he speaks during a news conference after being promoted to interim head coach, Monday, Oct. 5, 2015 in Davie, Fla. At rear is Mike Tannenbaum, left, Miami Dolphins executive vice president of football operations. Joe Philbin has been fired four games into his fourth season as coach of the Miami Dolphins, and one day after a flop on an international stage that helped to seal his fate. (AP Photo/Wilfredo Lee)
